xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 22, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rfl1665702797296.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rfl1665702797296.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rfl1665702797296.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rfl1665702797296\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Help Texts \n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this editor to create, edit, and delete help texts that can be displayed in a help window, to provide information about the application.\n </p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__note_w71ab1b7b1_w72ab1b7_w73ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Help texts are provided for backward compatibility. They are not recommended for modern applications.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__p_d6707e1_d6708e1_d6709e1\">Each help text must have a unique name; it cannot use the same name as a message or language setup.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__p_d6710e1_d6711e1_d6712e1\">Help texts can be accessed with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">help</span> ProcScript statement and the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$text</span> ProcScript function. New and updated help texts are automatically compiled when you save them.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__section_jm5_x5f_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1227707e70\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__ul_c3y_x5f_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__li_d3296e1_d3297e1_d3298e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__li_d3299e1_d3300e1_d3301e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cfv1665702708639.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cfv1665702708639.html\" title=\"Language code for the global object with which you are working.\">Language</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__li_d3302e1_d3303e1_d3304e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__li_d3305e1_d3306e1_d3307e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ohe1665702709579.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ohe1665702709579.html\" title=\"The text of the message, help text, language setup, panel or other global object.\">Text</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__li_d3308e1_d3309e1_d3310e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euc1665702808913.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euc1665702808913.html\" title=\"Horizontal position of the help text window, expressed as the number of character cells from the left of the application window.\">Left</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ebt1665702808983.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ebt1665702808983.html\" title=\"Width of the help text window, expressed as the number character cells.\">Width</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ukn1665702809052.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ukn1665702809052.html\" title=\"Vertical position of the help window, expressed as the number of character cells from the top of the application window.\">Top</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vvb1665702809126.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vvb1665702809126.html\" title=\"Height of the help text window, expressed as the number of character cells.\">Depth</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__li_d3311e1_d3312e1_d3313e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bck1665702654827.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bck1665702654827.html\" title=\"Extended description of the global object.\">Comments</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__section_ix5_y5f_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1227707e155\">How to</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__p_d6719e1_d6720e1_d6721e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sxb1705569063728.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sxb1705569063728.html\" title=\"Define help texts to create large blocks of text that can be displayed in a Uniface help window.\">Working with Help Texts</a>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__section_yxw_z5f_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1227707e171\">Menu Options</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Menu Options for Message Libraries</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__1\">Menu Option </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__2\">Action </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Open/New</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__2\">Open or create a new library. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Compile</span></span>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Compile all</span></span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">File &gt; Compile modified</span></span>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__2\">Compile the current, all, or modified global objects.\n              </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit &gt; New <var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;Global Object Type&gt; </var>\n</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__2\">Create a new global object. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit &gt; Duplicate <var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;Global Object Type&gt;</var>\n</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__2\">Save a copy of the current global object under a\n                different name. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Edit &gt; Delete <var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;Global Object Type&gt;</var>\n</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__2\">Delete the current global object. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View &gt;Zoom Field</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__2\">Edit the selected field in a separate dialog; useful\n                when editing text blocks and code. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">View &gt;Message Frame</span></span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__2\">Display the message frame; useful after compiling the\n                object.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Go To</span>\n<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;Global Object Type&gt;</var>\n</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rfl1665702797296__table_d578e1_d579e1_d580e1__entry__2\">Create or open a different type of global object, or\n                library (properties).</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hir1705568318852.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Messages</a><p>Messages are language-related objects that enable you to deploy a Uniface application in different languages and locales. They are stored in language-specific libraries, and Uniface automatically chooses the appropriate library at runtime based on the configuration.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zks1720074466587.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>help</a><p>Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531572\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531572\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Help Texts Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Help Texts Use this editor to create, edit, and delete help texts that can be displayed in a help window, to provide information about the application. Note: Help texts are provided for backward compatibility. They are not recommended for modern applications. Each help text must have a unique name; it cannot use the same name as a message or language setup. Help texts can be accessed with the help ProcScript statement and the $text ProcScript function. New and updated help texts are automatically compiled when you save them. Properties Name Language Description Text Left , Width , Top , Depth Comments How to Working with Help Texts Menu Options Table 1. Menu Options for Message Libraries Menu Option Action File > Open/New Open or create a new library. File > Compile File > Compile all File > Compile modified Compile the current, all, or modified global objects. Edit > New <Global Object Type> Create a new global object. Edit > Duplicate <Global Object Type> Save a copy of the current global object under a different name. Edit > Delete <Global Object Type> Delete the current global object. View >Zoom Field Edit the selected field in a separate dialog; useful when editing text blocks and code. View >Message Frame Display the message frame; useful after compiling the object. Go To <Global Object Type> Create or open a different type of global object, or library (properties). Related Links Messages Messages are language-related objects that enable you to deploy a Uniface application in different languages and locales. They are stored in language-specific libraries, and Uniface automatically chooses the appropriate library at runtime based on the configuration. help Display help information, either a Uniface help message or information from the native help system. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}